    <abstract id="aspace_0814e19c10d78be00278ccc888b2685e">This collection consists of eight letters written by Lucy Maria Tappan Bowen to her husband, Henry Bowen, and her sister, Susan Barney. Lucy Maria Tappan Bowen is more well-known as one of the women with whom Henry Ward Beecher had allegedly had an affair in the early 1860s, around the time some of these letters were written.</abstract>
